  "texts": [
    "The residual connections allow the model to learn features across multiple layers efficiently, capturing the intricate spatial patterns of remote sensing images.",
    "Meanwhile, the SE network Fig. 2 Workflow chart of the proposed system including the residual block and channel attention layers 123 selectively emphasizes spatial features relevant to scene classification, overcoming CNNs' inherent limitation of neglecting fine-grained, channel-specific information.",
    "Together, these mechanisms ensure that the RCA network is more robust and effective in capturing both local and global dependencies, making it superior to traditional CNN-based approaches in remote sensing image classification.The proposed RCA network introduces several key innovations for improving remote sensing image classification.",
    "These contributions are as follows:• Self-Attention-Based Deep Network: We introduce a novel self-attention deep network structure that incorporates a channel-attention mechanism within a residual convolutional network.",
    "This mechanism enables the model to focus on the most critical image regions while reducing background interference, resulting in improved classification performance, particularly for images with complex backgrounds."
  ]
}